<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Event Cancelled</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #ef4444; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
        .content { background: #fef2f2; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
        .event-details { background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; font-size: 14px; color: #666; }
        .alert { background: #fee2e2; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; border-left: 4px solid #ef4444; margin: 20px 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>‚ùå Event Cancelled</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello <strong>{{userName}}</strong>,</p>
        
        <div class="alert">
            <p><strong>Important Notice:</strong> We regret to inform you that <strong>{{eventTitle}}</strong> has been cancelled.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="event-details">
            <h3>üìÖ Cancelled Event</h3>
            <p><strong>Event:</strong> {{eventTitle}}</p>
            <p><strong>Reason:</strong> {{reason}}</p>
        </div>
        
        <p>We sincerely apologize for any inconvenience this may cause. We understand that you may have made arrangements to attend this event.</p>
        
        <p><strong>What happens next:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Your registration has been automatically cancelled</li>
            <li>If you paid for this event, a full refund will be processed within 5-7 business days</li>
            <li>You will be notified of any rescheduled dates if applicable</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>We appreciate your understanding and hope to see you at future events.</p>
        
        <p>If you have any questions or concerns, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>Best regards,<br>The One Event Team</p>
        <p><small>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</small></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
